dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Outagamie County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads and right of ways for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2018. These feature classes are located within the geodatabase Outagamie_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb. Roads: [Outagamie County Street Centerline Data.] ROW: [This is a polygon feature class representing the right of way boundaries within Outagamie County.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
